title: Star Wars: Imperial Military Personnel Stories (I.M.P.S.)
description:
Star Wars: Imperial Military Personnel Stories (I.M.P.S.)


I.M.P.S. The Relentless - Chapter 1: Davenport Gateway	(2005),	720x480,	0:21:18

Davenport Gateway is the first chapter in a seven part series that transitions from the Troops/Cops parody into the more mockumentary style as we join a patrol squad from the Imperial Urban Army on their final assignment for the day. Not a job for the lighthearted, these hardened soldiers put their lives on the line as they clean up the dark streets and dangerous corridors of Davenport Gateway.


I.M.P.S. The Relentless - Chapter 2: Norca System	(2010),	720x480,	0:22:58

In Chapter 2, aboard The Relentless in hyperspace, we arrive at the remote Norca System and deploy with the cold climate assault trooper division. This is the second part to a seven chapter series where we meet imperial drop ship pilots, along with the heavy armored assault crew that transport the snow troopers into their mission objective point
